  "description": "A hydrothermal vent erupting from the ocean floor. Bio exciter at maximum rate (0.5 Hz) with high brightness (4000 Hz) creates rapid staccato bursts above the sub foundation — mineral-rich superheated water shooting upward. The waveguide body in wreck mode adds metallic chimney resonance. LFO1 at 0.3 Hz modulates bio rate for irregular eruption patterns. The CREATURE macro controls eruption intensity from gentle seep to violent geyser.",
